{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_013obV4jgdbnQ5HtpFPijW9i","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Now I have a clear picture. The approach:\n\n1. Add `tracing` and `tracing-subscriber` to Cargo.toml\n2. Initialize tracing subscriber in `main()` \n3. Replace `println!` in `src/gui/mod.rs` with `tracing::info!`\n4. Replace `eprintln!` in `src/config/manager.rs` with `tracing::warn!`\n\nThe `src/ui/` and `src/inspect/` println calls are intentional user-facing CLI output — those stay as-is."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":367,"cache_read_input_tokens":54434,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":367},"output_tokens":3,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"c9bd7957-c8f2-4e48-8fcc-7059d242854c","uuid":"eb1e6e88-e4f3-4efc-8c98-a67665c0e85d"}
